{
  "stem": "18770.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 72.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, and there would be drills where the windows were covered up, you know, when they would-- and lights had to be turned off.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The whole city would go dark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's a very unifying kind of an experience.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's a feeling of that something very big is happening, and you're part of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We would have maps up, you know, in our--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the American experience.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we have the maps up on the wall with the pins showing how the Allied troops are advancing, and of they've landed in Sicily.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're moving here, and this is what's happening in the Pacific.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All that's very, very exciting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then there is the more tragic sense of the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's coming through what I'm picking up primarily from my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because my mother's side of the family has mostly gotten out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I see my father's life, first of all, very dislocated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I see him having one heart attack then another heart attack, being very, very unhappy-- not in a land where he's comfortable, not in a life that he's comfortable in, and not feeling like there are many choices for him to start again.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have-- I have sort of memories of him writing and trying to find out about his family, and, you know, and not having success with that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I see his humiliation in the-- in the workplace with my uncles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That-- those are all consequences of the war, you know, which are affecting his life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They're affecting me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm, for whatever exact reasons-- partially my sensitivity and God knows what else-- I actually develop an ulcer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm only 12 years old, and I get an ulcer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Kids at 12 generally do not get ulcers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So obviously, I've been very sensitive to what has happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
